languages.text: "Мое дело не языком молоть, а за такими, как ты, приглядывать".
"I'm not paid to talk. I'm paid to watch characters like you."
languages.original_text: "Мое дело не языком молоть, а за такими, как ты, приглядывать".

traits.locale_text: "I'm not paid to talk. I'm paid to watch characters like you."
"I'm not paid to talk. I'm paid to watch characters like you."

languages.text: “我不是收钱来这里闲聊的，我负责留意像你这样的人。”
languages.original_text: "I'm not paid to talk. I'm paid to watch characters like you."

traits.locale_text: “我从来不在喝酒的时候谈生意。”

languages.text: «No me pagan por hablar, sino por vigilar a gente como usted».
languages.original_text: "I'm not paid to talk. I'm paid to watch characters like you."

traits.locale_text: «No me pagan por hablar, sino por vigilar a gente como usted».

languages.text: 「俺の仕事はおしゃべりじゃない。お前のようなヤツを見張るのが仕事なんだ」
languages.original_text: "I'm not paid to talk. I'm paid to watch characters like you."

traits.locale_text: 「俺の仕事はおしゃべりじゃない。お前のようなヤツを見張るのが仕事なんだ」

languages.text: "Ich werde nicht fürs Reden bezahlt. Ich werde bezahlt, um Leute wie Euch zu beobachten."
languages.original_text: "I'm not paid to talk. I'm paid to watch characters like you."

traits.locale_text: "Ich rede nicht übers Geschäft, wenn ich trinke."

languages.text: « On ne me paie pas pour bavarder, mais pour surveiller les individus de votre acabit. »
languages.original_text: "I'm not paid to talk. I'm paid to watch characters like you."

traits.locale_text: « Je parle pas affaires quand je bois. »

languages.text: "Konuşmak için para almıyorum. Senin gibileri izlemek için alıyorum."
languages.original_text: "I'm not paid to talk. I'm paid to watch characters like you."

traits.locale_text: "Konuşmak için para almıyorum. Senin gibileri izlemek için alıyorum."
